       "            rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://xgboost.readthedocs.io/en/release_3.2.0/python/python_api.html#xgboost.XGBClassifier#:~:text=verbosity,-typing.Optional%5Bint%5D\">\n",
